\[\lambda(\widehat{\bm{\Sigma}}+\lambda I_{p})^{-1}\simeq(v(-\lambda;\gamma)\bm{ \Sigma}+\bm{I}_{p})^{-1},\]

_where \(v(-\lambda;\gamma)>0\) is the unique solution to the fixed-point equation_

\[\frac{1}{v(-\lambda;\gamma)}=\lambda+\gamma\int\frac{r}{1+v(-\lambda;\gamma)r} \,\,\mathrm{d}H_{p}(r).\] (40)

